## **MCP Server Integration**

### **Environment Configuration**
```bash
# ✅ DO: Set required environment variables
export SHOPIFY_ACCESS_TOKEN="shpat_your_token_here"
export MYSHOPIFY_DOMAIN="vividwalls-2.myshopify.com"
export THEME_WORKSPACE="./themes"
```

### **Theme Development Tools**
```bash
# ✅ DO: Use comprehensive MCP tools
theme-create --name "vividwalls-theme" --template "dawn"
theme-file-write --directory "./themes/vividwalls" --filePath "snippets/vividwalls-inventory-widget.liquid"
theme-file-create --fileType "section" --templateName "product-section"
theme-search-replace --searchPattern "old-class" --replacement "vividwalls-class"
```

